{"tid":431184,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"細路版紅樓夢又幾好睇","createTime":"2017-10-10T12:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T14:00:58.000Z","uid":82558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"89e184426b15b160a11ccd69949f43f75a28fde3","tid":431184,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"紅樓夢本身係四大名著入面改拍為電視劇都幾難（邊有咁易搵咁多靚女），對上一套10年版翻拍到好似鬼片溝紀錄片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家呢套搵啲細路仔拍，啲妹妹好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，啲戲又唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最緊要符合原著年齡（搵個三四十扮林妹妹睇見都想死喇）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/204138_6dc1093452a2bf1e452c3f1ade775a88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F204138_6dc1093452a2bf1e452c3f1ade775a88.png&h=7b8cfce5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c902afd2b4bbf7874ee9de4b5bd88b90f6ada73c","tid":431184,"uid":82558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"林妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/204749_37d473e6ddd9a12d2adf7c748e2ee2ef.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F204749_37d473e6ddd9a12d2adf7c748e2ee2ef.jpeg&h=c0dfcda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王熙鳳全劇最好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/204806_5ca8a20942d7dbce13061dc08f60b4c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F204806_5ca8a20942d7dbce13061dc08f60b4c0.png&h=c40a469b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四春姐妹（最靚元春，做貴妃嗰個）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/204807_286625b73e1427d68628ca22539f68f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F204807_286625b73e1427d68628ca22539f68f8.jpg&h=6d95d687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶釵bb有啲baby fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/205109_57decbc5007cbddbc9277e14cdf0d38b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F205109_57decbc5007cbddbc9277e14cdf0d38b.jpeg&h=3a7000a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個人最鍾意大嫂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/205358_82bec42861e112daee926df3f285b517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F205358_82bec42861e112daee926df3f285b517.png&h=9c1a7964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbea307d86450c4b765353111f595ad951f65b95","tid":431184,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"紅樓夢搵咁細個拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fd5756fe4b515f9f9df9826218cb786399bf96","tid":431184,"uid":39866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"戀童 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ed353e55a6c46dc14950afcb1549120bded21","tid":431184,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅樓夢搵咁細個拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真講，林黛玉入賈府十一二歲咋"},{"pid":"79fa364155132132540736cafa10c182b60370de","tid":431184,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":